title: FDHypno-Audio_Compilation_2
description:
Sample audio files from 9 female hypnotists. Something for everyone in the audience, I guess.

I particularly like Katana and the included file is available free on her website. I would really like to hear some more of her work if anyone out there has some. Also included is Soforia who apparently died last year; at least I read that somewhere. Her style can be described as "different" as can Evilena.
To my ear Miss Drew, who features on Dominica's website, sounds amazingly similar to Queen Passionate who - wait for it - formerly featured on the same site but is no longer mentioned. 
Also featured here are Inamorata (sexy) and Deseree as well as the extraordinary Mistress of Hypnosis who also calls herself Queen Kathleen.
Have fun but watch out: it's a jungle out there.
